{"tid":2323253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"200萬中共党員大規模滲透輝瑞、滙豐、波音、英國領館...","createTime":"2020-12-13T04:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T15:35:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":60,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d1074b3e9b3ae76110de60847f21c279a3c851","tid":2323253,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"由全球多國共150名議員組成的「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」，近日取得一份195萬名中共黨員的名單，顯示中共黨員已遍布眾多大型跨國企業及外國駐中使領館。包括研發武漢肺炎疫苗的藥廠輝瑞、阿斯特捷利康，涉及國防航太的企業如波音、空中巴士、勞斯萊斯，涉及凍結香港異議人士帳戶的滙豐、渣打銀行，以及英國駐上海總領事館等，都有中共黨員任職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201213/FY7NTP3DKBESPAO3II536KGM6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201213%2FFY7NTP3DKBESPAO3II536KGM6U%2F&d=S6zCjV1yqQRAjAhc4t20mdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=c945e51f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201213%2FFY7NTP3DKBESPAO3II536KGM6U%2F&h=5e0b2150\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201213/FY7NTP3DKBESPAO3II536KGM6U/</a>"},{"pid":"84d3fda0cb5557fdadcbee091bea6ef44a706cd2","tid":2323253,"uid":35236,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"宜家先知遲唔遲d"},{"pid":"bae42ce43ca72e73240e05a3cf8b0550bd48bc45","tid":2323253,"uid":304916,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"千人計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e355eb659c4c5a50fbc3b18d7811bfbe863c1c4","tid":2323253,"uid":103230,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:14:10.000Z","msg":"200萬個間諜<br />\n嚇撚死歐美未<br />\n仲係度同中共傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5216f406d3d103e3df7436896da102435c67991","tid":2323253,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T05:19:58.000Z","msg"